    • loadKnownSlots

      public void loadKnownSlots​(java.lang.String pKnownSlotsFile) throws org.apache.uima.resource.ResourceInitializationException
      loadKnownSlots loads the known slots from the resource url. The format for knownSlots is slotName|[true|false|sectionName] false if this is a name to block from being recognized as a name SectionName if this is a known section name, even though it looks like a slot name.
      Parameters:
      pKnownSlotsFile -
      Throws:
      org.apache.uima.resource.ResourceInitializationException - if loading of patterns fails.
